---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="My Story - raymondreamer">
   <main class="bg-black min-h-screen py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
         <div class="backdrop-blur-lg bg-black/60 p-12 rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <div class="space-y-16">
               <!-- Header -->
               <div class="space-y-2 mb-12">
                  <p class="text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs">My Story</p>
                  <h1 class="font-russo text-5xl font-bold bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-400">
                     The Journey of a Creative Developer
                  </h1>
               </div>

               <!-- Story Content -->
               <div class="space-y-12 text-lg">
                  <div class="space-y-6">
                     <h2 class="font-russo text-2xl font-bold mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-400">
                        Early Beginnings
                     </h2>
                     <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        My journey began in Minnesota, where I discovered my entrepreneurial spirit early on. At 12, I combined my passion for skateboarding with self-taught coding skills to create and sell custom skateboards online. This early venture sparked my lifelong dedication to merging creativity with technical innovation.
                     </p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="space-y-6">
                     <h2 class="font-russo text-2xl font-bold mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-400">
                        Professional Evolution
                     </h2>
                     <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        For over 15 years, I've been at the intersection of technology and creative design, specializing in high-fidelity prototyping, 3D design, and sophisticated content management systems. My work combines technical expertise with artistic vision, allowing me to build immersive web experiences that bridge the gap between functionality and innovation.
                     </p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="space-y-6">
                     <h2 class="font-russo text-2xl font-bold mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-400">
                        Current Focus
                     </h2>
                     <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Currently, I'm building Rthmn, a cutting-edge data visualization technology for trading markets that transforms complex financial data into intuitive, geometric patterns. Alongside this, I've created Reality Designers, an online community and blog focused on consciousness exploration and personal development, bringing together thousands of individuals interested in expanding their understanding of reality.
                     </p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="space-y-6">
                     <h2 class="font-russo text-2xl font-bold mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-400">
                        Beyond the Code
                     </h2>
                     <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        When I'm not coding or creating 3D art, you'll find me skateboarding along the San Diego coast or exploring new ways to push the boundaries of digital creation. Based between Silicon Valley and San Diego, I continue to seek out projects that challenge the status quo and create meaningful digital experiences.
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </div>

               <!-- Contact CTA -->
               <div class="pt-12 border-t border-white/10">
                  <a href="mailto:your@email.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white hover:text-white/80">
                     <span class="font-light">Let's work together</span>
                     <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
                     </svg>
                  </a>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </main>
</Layout>
